body:
by **tav@espians.com**:

<pre>In http/fs.go, serveFile() sets a Content-Type header of &quot;text-plain;
charset=utf-8&quot;
when the file content looks like utf-8 encoded text.

I'm pretty sure that this should be &quot;text/plain; charset=utf-8&quot; ?

<a href="http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3676">http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3676</a></pre>
